snippet.title: Cones and Spheres [ACT 3]: How Many Cones Does It Take To Fill a Sphere?
snippet.description:
http://tapintoteenminds.com/3act-math/cones-and-spheres/ Learn about the volume relationship between cones and spheres.  How many cones will it take to fill up the sphere?  This video will answer that question for you and help us try to visualize and derive the formula for Volume of a Sphere.

This is the third act of a 3 act math task called "Cones and Spheres"
